        "\n",
        "### 🫩 Sooo much data!\n",
        "\n",
        ":::{.fragment}\n",
        "\n",
        "- The amount of data being collected, stored, and processed is [growing exponentially]{.accent}!\n",
        "\n",
        "- Larger variety of [increasingly complicated]{.accent} data types.\n",
        "\n",
        ":::\n",
        "\n",
        ":::{.fragment}\n",
        "\n",
